==Gems on Windows
http://stevenharman.net/blog/archive/2008/11/12/installing-rubygems-in-cygwin.aspx

$ pkg-install.exe http://rubyforge.org/projects/rubygems
$ unpack.exe ruby.tar.gz
$ ruby.exe setup.rb install
$ gem.exe update --system


   3. In a bash terminal, navigate to the unpacked directory
   4. Run the following command:

      ruby setup.rb install

   5. Update RubyGems by running the following: 


